'''Surgical shock''' is the [[shock (circulatory)|shock]] to the [[circulatory system|circulation]] resulting from [[surgery]].  It is commonly due to a [[bleeding|loss of blood]] which results in insufficient [[blood volume]].<ref name=CCL/>

